, that what is between east and west is the direction of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28156,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/salat-al-witr-ahl-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":31704,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Witr prayer recommended, not obligation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali ibn Abi Talib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah is numerically odd and He loves what is odd, so perform the Witr prayer, O people of the Quran!\u201d Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThe Witr\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8238,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/ali-ibn-abu-talib-cursed\/","url_meta":{"origin":31704,"position":2},"title":"Ali on Curses: Those who curse others are themselves cursed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubayd al-Kindi reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThose who curse others are themselves cursed.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 315 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0628\u064a\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0643\u0646\u062f\u064a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u200f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u200f \u0639\u0644\u064a \u0628\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0637\u0627\u0644\u0