lyhadithonline\/2022\/09\/28\/allahu-alam\/","url_meta":{"origin":31704,"position":4},"title":"Ali on Ignorance: When to say Allah knows best","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 28, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Razin Abi al-Nu\u2019man reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWhen you are asked about what you do not know, then flee.\u201d It was said, \u201cO leader of the faithful, how does one flee?\u201d Ali said, \u201cThat you say: Allah knows best.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24287,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/01\/22\/ali-sabr-iman-head-body\/","url_meta":{"origin":31704,"position":5},"title":"Ali on Sabr: Patience to faith like a head to a body","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Masruq reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, patience is to faith as the head is to the body. If the head is cut, the body will perish.\u201d Then, Ali raised his voice and he said, \u201cNo doubt, there is no faith for one\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/31704","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/p